                        <interp inst="t18480515-name-1246" type="given" value="ANDREW"></interp>ANDREW DOUGLASS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I took the prisoner a Charlton—I told him the charge—he said, "I expected as much."</p>
